============
Introduction
============

Personal site and blog at https://windsornguyen.com.

Built with TanStack Start, Vite, and Nitro; MDX for content; Supabase for
view counts.

==========
Running it
==========

-------------
Prerequisites
-------------

- Node 22 or newer
- pnpm 10 or newer
- Supabase CLI (only for `pnpm db` commands)
- SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY in the environment

---------
Procedure
---------

 $ pnpm install
 $ pnpm dev

Open http://localhost:3000.

===========
Conventions
===========

Repo conventions (MDX shape, design tokens, env files, CSS specificity)
live in AGENTS.md.

